The best way to twist is this.

Make hotkeys of the songs, meaning put the spell gem on the top left, 2 to the right of that, 3rd on the left again, ect.

Push 1..then RIGHT when the song has ended and hit 2 to stop the song from continuing, then 2 to start the song..wait till RIGHT when it ends and hit 3 to stop the song, then 3 to begin the new song.

So it goes like this. 1...2,2...3,3..4,4...1,1..ect.

Get it?

  

